  VPN > VPNTunnel > VPNTunnelEndpoint hierarchy. Member IPs and protected                                                                                                                                                                        
  networks now use native fields (source_ipaddress, protected_prefixes).                                                                                                                                                                         
  PSK stored in 1Password via onepassword-sdk, referenced through Nautobot                                                                                                                                                                       
  Secrets framework.                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 
  - Add data migration creating 4 custom fields + "Member VPN Endpoint" DeviceType                                                                                                                                                               
  - Add 1Password SDK integration for PSK storage (onepassword_utils.py)                                                                                                                                                                         
  - Refactor api/views.py: full object hierarchy creation (VPN, VPNTunnel,                                                                                                                                                                       
    VPNProfile clone, member Device with dummy0, hub/spoke endpoints)                                                                                                                                                                            
  - Refactor api/serializers.py: new fields (member_name, location_city/state,                                                                                                                                                                   
    template_vpn_profile, hub/member_protected_prefix)                                                                                                                                                                                           
  - Refactor jobs.py: PortalBuildIpsecTunnel reads from native objects                                                                                                                                                                           
